title: Dr M: Muhyiddin's praise not intended for Najib's Umno
text:
More 
When Parti Pribumi Bersatu Malaysia (Bersatu) president Muhyiddin Yassin admitted that Umno and BN had developed Malaysia, Dr Mahathir Mohamad claimed that Prime Minister Najib Abdul Razak's apple polishers were ecstatic. 
The Bersatu chairperson said despite Muhyiddin making the statement in referrence to Umno and BN of the past, these individuals took it as a compliment to the present administration.
